flowchart LR
    A[Propose use and decision purpose] --> B[Classify consequence, data, and population]
    B --> C[Review necessity, validity, privacy, security, and legal risk]
    C --> D{Approve?}
    D -->|No| E[Reject or redesign]
    E --> A
    D -->|Yes| F[Register use, controls, owner, and expiration]
    F --> G[Implement least privilege, quality gates, notice, and appeal]
    G --> H[Monitor access, drift, misuse, subgroup effects, and incidents]
    H --> I{Continue use?}
    I -->|Modify| A
    I -->|Suspend| J[Contain, investigate, and correct]
    J --> H
    I -->|Retire| K[Revoke access, delete or archive data, preserve decision record]
    I -->|Yes| L[Periodic recertification]
    L --> H

    Q[Audit, provenance, correction, rollback, and practitioner participation] -. applies throughout .-> B
    Q -. applies throughout .-> G
    Q -. applies throughout .-> H
    Q -. applies throughout .-> K
